  "prompt": "Who sings a song titled \"Home\"?",
  "response": "There are several artists who have sung songs titled \"Home.\" Here are a few examples:\n\n1. **Michael Bubl\u00e9** - His version of \"Home\" was released in 2005 and became one of his signature songs.\n2. **Phillip Phillips** - He released \"Home\" as the debut single from his album \"The World from the Side of the Moon\" in 2012, which gained significant popularity after his American Idol win.\n3. **Edward Sharpe and the Magnetic Zeros** - They have a song called \"Home\" from their 2010 album \"Up from Below.\"\n4. **Daughtry** - Their song \"Home\" is from the album \"Daughtry\" released in 2006.\n\nThese are just a few examples, and there may be other artists with songs by the same title.",
